            Corporate Events FAQ
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <details class="card group">
              <summary class="font-bold text-brand-white cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
                Do you offer invoicing for corporate bookings?
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-orange group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                </svg>
              </summary>
              <p class="text-brand-gray mt-3">
                Yes! We can invoice your company directly and work with your procurement or accounting department. We accept purchase orders and can provide itemized receipts for expense reporting.
              </p>
            </details>

            <details class="card group">
              <summary class="font-bold text-brand-white cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
                Can we customize the event for our team?
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-orange group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                </svg>
              </summary>
              <p class="text-brand-gray mt-3">
                Absolutely! We can design custom team-building tournaments, create company-branded experiences, and tailor the event format to your specific goals. Contact us to discuss your vision.
              </p>
            </details>

            <details class="card group">
              <summary class="font-bold text-brand-white cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
                What's included in the team building package?
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-orange group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path>
                </svg>
              </summary>
              <p class="text-brand-gray mt-3">
                Our team building packages include dedicated event coordination, customized team challenges or tournaments, private gaming space, and optional catering. We design activities to promote collaboration, communication, and friendly competition.
              </p>
            </details>

            <details class="card group">
              <summary class="font-bold text-brand-white cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
                How far in advance should we book?
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-orange group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
